ioedata.sensordata.model

Class SensorDataValue

  • java.lang.Object
    • ioedata.sensordata.model.SensorDataValue

  • public final class SensorDataValue
extends java.lang.Object
    This class creates data transport objects that contain the sensor data timestamp, the raw data from sensors and the respective sensor information. Also, it can contain an array data information to represent a list of the past raw sensor data.
    Author:
    ajou
